Install venv support (once):
sudo apt update
sudo apt install -y python3-venv python3-pip

Go to your project folder:
cd /path/to/your/project

Create the environment:
python3 -m venv RL_learning

Activate it:
source RL_learning/bin/activate

Upgrade pip (recommended):
python -m pip install --upgrade pip

To leave the environment later:
deactivate

so far the best run command is:
python train_reaction_reinforce.py --gscdb-root ../../GSCDB --out-dir ../models/reaction_reinforce_mae_plus --warmup-supervised 3000 --emae-steps 2500 --steps 2500 --reward-mode regret --select-best-by mae --lr 0.003 --entropy-coef 0.005 --batch-size 256 --hidden 512 256

to plot
python plot_training_curves.py --history ../models/reaction_reinforce_mae_plus/training_history.json


